summary: Adds a dirt wagon path to Heljarchen.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds an access road to Heljarchen Hall. I thought it odd that you have this great home up on a hill but no road to it. So I made one. Nothing fancy, just a dirt road. If you're wondering at the width of the road, just imagine wagons using it to deliver their loads of building materials.

Do not use with Heljarchen Farm as they modify the same area and could cause a CTD.
